name: Founding Full Stack Engineer
content:

name: [OM GANDHI] - Software Engineer
content:
We believe in the power of people. Because the potential for people to do something outstanding has everything to do with being in the right role, on the right team, at the right time. That’s where Paraform Integration Sandbox comes in.

We are looking for a motivated, dedicated and self-starting founding engineer to join Complete.

This is more of a (product [https://posthog.com/blog/what-is-a-product-engineer] or growth [https://posthog.com/blog/what-is-a-growth-engineer] engineering role rather than traditional software engineering in that we want you to have a lot of ownership in what you build

This is a full-stack role and we use a variety of modern technologies including Next.js, Vercel, Typescript.

We're looking for our second Engineer and would work closely with the co-founders, especially the CTO (Pochahontas), along with our founding engineer to develop our core product of enabling a recruiter-driven marketplace.

We offer a full slate of benefits from competitive salaries, stock options, fully paid options for health coverage (medical, dental and vision), disability coverage, employer paid life insurance, mental health resources, financial wellness benefits, and a fully paid parental leave program. For US-based employees, we offer flexible vacation and a 401(k) matching program.
